name: BIG APPLE
description: I just love to travel to BIG APPLE again! Most majestic chaos I have ever witnessed! I don't like crowded places but from the moment I stepped from Aishuttle to Grand Central, I felt like I play in some movie. So familiar places and so many people on the streets. I almost started to cry that I finally traveled into this amazing city. SUch a buildings and so many architectural wonders, museums, restaurants and of course heart of the city Central Park.
